      "rdfs:label": "Four-Stroke Engine (Poclet)",
      "rdfs:comment": "Minimal yet complete system representation of the thermodynamic cycle powering internal combustion engines. Demonstrates all 5 ASFID dimensions through 4 sequential strokes and mobilizes 20 M2 GenericConcepts (v15.10.1). Canonical example for cyclic processes and energy transformation.",
