      },
      "m0:changelog": [
        {
          "version": "1.2.0",
          "date": "2026-03-18",
          "changes": [
            "Aligned to M2 v15.10.1: Cycle→(Process+FeedbackLoop), Sequence→Workflow, Flow→Channel, Synchronization→Alignment; m2:Efficiency moved to M1_Thermodynamics (domain-specific)",
            "Added @base declaration; prefixes m3/m2/m1core now use short relative IRIs",
            "Fixed tensor formulas: 'x' → '⊗' throughout; GenericConceptCoverage updated to 20/75 (27%); added m3:ontologyCategory"
          ]
        },
        {
          "version": "1.1.0",
          "date": "2026-02-24",
          "changes": [
            "BREAKING: Corrected Map perspective acronym from ORIVE to REVOI (canonical TSCG notation)",
            "R renamed Representability (was Reproducibility); E renamed Evolvability (was Expressiveness); V renamed Verifiability (was Validity)",
            "Updated REVOI vector to (0.90, 0.85, 0.90, 0.90, 0.85); epistemic gap recalculated to 0.132; added m0:asfidScores, m0:revoiScores and m0:epistemicGap flat fields for poclet loader compatibility"
          ]
        },
        {
          "version": "1.0.1",
          "date": "2026-01-28",
          "changes": [
            "Added transdisciplinaryValidation section with 4 cross-domain examples; completed m1Contributions with 7 thermodynamics-specific concepts"
          ]
        }
